PART 7: SPECTRAL GAP RATIO — UNIVERSAL CONSTANT?
======================================================================

For Interval: Q_1/Q_2 appears to approach a universal constant ~9.
This ratio determines the 'expansion quality' of the tournament.

  p= 7: Q_1/Q_2 = 7.8509, Q_1 = 5.0489, Q_2 = 0.643104
  p=11: Q_1/Q_2 = 8.5205, Q_1 = 12.3435, Q_2 = 1.448691
